extendedInfo.description: A companion to Disney Edition's Birnbaum Guides to Walt Disney World, the Magic Kingdom Expert Quest challenges readers of Ridley Pearson's best-selling Kingdom Keepers series to complete a puzzling set of questions designed to test your knowledge of the Magic Kingdom at Walt Disney World and Kingdom Keepers: Disney After Dark in order to determine how close to a real Keeper you are yourself! Put on your thinking caps.

reviews.title: So much fun!
reviews.comment: I downloaded this app at Disney World and ran around with my nephew hunting down clues and solving the quest. It was lots of fun and a great way to see different parts of the park. And also a good tool to teach creative problem solving (and team work).
reviews.author: Jennifer Lou

reviews.title: Awesome quest!
reviews.comment: Most of the clues here were solvable at the park, and there\'s even a mode that lets you play it if you\'re not there (thoughtful for those of us that haven\'t made the trip yet). And for lovers of the book series, it\'s a bonus add on!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Wonderfully awsome grate for having a fun jorney all around.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great fun for kids!
reviews.comment: I played this with my cousin when we went to Disney World and we really enjoyed solving the clues in the park. It was definitely a good break from the rides when the lines got too long
reviews.author: Shayan Guha

reviews.title: A great idea!
reviews.comment: This app is super fun and a good way to experience the park in a new way. Very cool.
reviews.author: Melanie Downing
